{"tid":2300924,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"公營屋短缺 忽吹噓搵夠地","createTime":"2020-11-26T02:10:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T02:27:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ebfc01947a8ca2f69fcfc654886408d1d63efbc7","tid":2300924,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T02:10:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201126/4UG675CIY5BIJDMYAOFSS3PXYY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201126%2F4UG675CIY5BIJDMYAOFSS3PXYY%2F&d=Z5fxCpLMP6GgpQ63MmTuws3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=e20d0cdd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201126%2F4UG675CIY5BIJDMYAOFSS3PXYY%2F&h=c36d26ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201126/4UG675CIY5BIJDMYAOFSS3PXYY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n公營屋短缺 忽吹噓搵夠地<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VUAmk3KJJwRkMIpLzcCkuFrcqQw=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MKD53YTRJJHRFAFQFN45PHH4NY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVUAmk3KJJwRkMIpLzcCkuFrcqQw%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMKD53YTRJJHRFAFQFN45PHH4NY.jpg&h=6af7f44a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■房屋問題一直困擾不少港人，惟公屋建屋量至今沒一年達標。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【2020施政報告】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：向九萬輪候戶派錢「贖罪」<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】房屋供應是每年施政報告的重點，任內公屋輪候時間不斷延長、樓價高企不下，特首林鄭月娥不待下屬運輸及房屋局局長陳帆公佈最新一期《長遠房屋策略》，率先宣佈「成功爭取」未來十年公營房屋需求的單位已全數覓得用地。她又公佈小蠔灣港鐵車廠用地及港鐵北環綫地區建屋大計，預料可提供合共九萬個單位。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭表示，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：酒店賓館充當過渡房屋<br />\n<br />\n年前曾引起爭議的粉嶺高球場用地，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/s806LCSdyInEZKGl-ag97Z6mltY=/1670x1187/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PCZWTEQE5NER5INI5K4TNSTXTU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fs806LCSdyInEZKGl-ag97Z6mltY%3D%2F1670x1187%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPCZWTEQE5NER5INI5K4TNSTXTU.jpg&h=f1b5b1d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小蠔灣車廠上蓋擬建公屋<br />\n<br />\n其實今年施政報告公佈的增加土地的「新猷」不多，其中較有進展的為涉及鐵路項目的土地供應政策。當局稱將加緊落實北環綫鐵路項目，配合古洞北新發展區公營房屋入伙，及帶動新田、牛潭尾及凹頭一帶的發展。政府至今在沿線附近物色到總面積約90公頃的房屋用地進行研究，即相當於四個太古城的面積，當中包括新田/落馬洲樞紐，若落實北環綫，相關土地可望帶來逾七萬個房屋單位。<br />\n<br />\n政府消息稱，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n報告亦透露，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n政府消息指，。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"56fedfa123dcb6ab099259f61fce7496aba16db8","tid":2300924,"uid":217049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T02:14:04.000Z","msg":"林鄭2021都夠票連任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d4b5a962f6a641d6c3c25ebe355a49dbbfe64c","tid":2300924,"uid":354403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T02:14:11.000Z","msg":"咁明日大愚就可以唔洗起公屋"},{"pid":"898bda380f7027a1fabcbeba3bd306ad596dae19","tid":2300924,"uid":7452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T02:27:28.000Z","msg":"貧窮，殘疾，精神病，長期病患，吸毒，爛賭，酒精上癮，貧窮老人，邊青，黑幫，失業，失學，低學歷，低技術<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n公屋就係政府一次過將所有問題集中嘅地方 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6jZOR4b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6jZOR4b.gif&h=94dab9c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2785000/2785658/neighbor_thumb_20201024_S_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2785000%2F2785658%2Fneighbor_thumb_20201024_S_600.jpg&h=1b960db8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsG5EKCN.gif&amp;h=fc5bd30e&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MkptO4D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbn